'''HWA Gaming''' was a Turkish esports organization, founded in 2008. Besides LoL, they also had teams in Counter Strike 1.6, Call of Duty, Point Blank, FIFA, DotA 2, and racing games. '''HWA''' stands for '''Hardwarena'''

